1
00:01:10,799 --> 00:01:11,400
Your Highness,

2
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,599
the Secret Guard sent a message.

3
00:01:12,599 --> 00:01:13,400
Miss Meng Li

4
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:15,400
was forcibly taken to the Vice Minister's Mansion.

5
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:17,040
They're gonna kill her

6
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:18,879
to marry her to the dead son.

7
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:19,920
What?

8
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:30,680
The heaven has three wonders, the sun, the moon, and the stars.

9
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:35,680
The earth is transparent, and the ghosts and gods are startled.

10
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:46,359
If there are ghosts like wolves and tigers coming,

11
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:50,959
If there are ghosts like wolves and tigers coming,

12
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:53,319
the heaven is clear,

13
00:01:53,319 --> 00:01:55,439
The earth is spiritually alive.

14
00:01:55,599 --> 00:01:57,879
The auspicious hour has arrived.

15
00:01:57,879 --> 00:02:02,079
The bride and groom pay respects to heaven and earth.

16
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,479
Go!

17
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:25,479
Finally, I've waited for the moment when you're alone.

18
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,759
You killed so many of our companions.

19
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:28,800
Today,

20
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:31,280
you will pay back with your life.

21
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,120
Seeking death.

22
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,599
First, bow to heaven and earth.

23
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:17,039
Second, bow to the elders.

24
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:25,560
Third, the couple bows to each other.

25
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,439
[So it's him.]

26
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:58,800
[My son seems very pleased with his wife.]

27
00:04:02,599 --> 00:04:04,400
[Like two blossoms in bloom,]

28
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,560
[they are bound together.]

29
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,919
[Drums and music resound,]

30
00:04:07,919 --> 00:04:09,599
[candles cast a festive glow.]

31
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:12,000
[They drink the cross-cupped wine.]

32
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:44,360
[In the afterlife,]

33
00:04:44,839 --> 00:04:46,639
[take good care of my son.]

34
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:02,920
[My son,]

35
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:05,160
[you can rest in peace.]

36
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,720
[The ceremony is complete.]

37
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,600
[Enter the bridal chamber!]

38
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,360
Li!

39
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,319
Shen Que,

40
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,240
where are you?

41
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,879
[It was my fault.]

42
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:19,040
[I shouldn't have trusted others with my safety.]

43
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:23,759
[The only one who can save me]

44
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:27,399
[is myself.]

45
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,480
Zha...

46
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:49,639
Zha...

47
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,040
Zha...

48
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:51,639
Zha...

49
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:52,639
You're back from the dead?

50
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:33,920
How dare you!

51
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:36,279
A mere orphan from a theatrical troupe,

52
00:07:36,279 --> 00:07:37,639
how dare you oppose me?

53
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:41,000
The real orphan

54
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:44,399
was killed by your son, Ruan Wei.

55
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,000
Who are you, really?

56
00:07:50,279 --> 00:07:51,759
Rather than who I am,

57
00:07:52,759 --> 00:07:55,959
you'd want to know how Ruan Wei died, right?

58
00:07:58,759 --> 00:07:59,759
Wei, what's wrong?

59
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,600
What are you doing?

60
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:03,319
Shut up!

61
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,560
Watch the show.

62
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,720
From now on, I am you.

63
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:10,600
Stop pretending to be noble.

64
00:08:11,079 --> 00:08:12,959
You bully innocent people like this.

65
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,319
Aren't you afraid of being caught?

66
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:15,439
Hmph.

67
00:08:16,879 --> 00:08:18,480
I'm the son of the Vice Minister.

68
00:08:19,439 --> 00:08:21,279
You're just an orphan from a theater troupe.

69
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,800
How dare you fight with me?

70
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,480
What do you want to do?

71
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,159
Now,

72
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,279
it's your turn.

73
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:48,200
This is my gift for you.

74
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,279
Do you like it?

75
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:05,039
Misfortune and fortune are not predestined.

76
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,960
They are brought by oneself.

77
00:09:08,519 --> 00:09:10,000
Good and evil are rewarded

78
00:09:10,399 --> 00:09:11,840
like shadows following their owners.

79
00:09:11,919 --> 00:09:15,200
I... I know I was wrong.

80
00:09:15,559 --> 00:09:18,000
Please let me go.

81
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:19,960
The wedding ceremony hasn't started yet.

82
00:09:20,519 --> 00:09:21,679
You want to leave now?

83
00:09:34,759 --> 00:09:35,639
Next,

84
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,600
cross-cupped wine.

85
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,200
Please,

86
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,440
spare us!

87
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,440
I'm sorry!

88
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:57,120
I really am!

89
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:01,840
Let...

90
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:03,720
Let me go!

91
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,600
To be free,

92
00:10:07,519 --> 00:10:08,799
it's quite simple.

93
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,240
I'm late.

94
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,399
I was too forward.

95
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,840
Sorry for the trouble.

96
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:45,000
Forgive me.

97
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,519
Have we grown

98
00:10:47,559 --> 00:10:48,840
so distant?

99
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,519
I failed to protect you.

100
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,639
Go change your clothes.

101
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:56,799
Once outside,

102
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:57,840
I'll carry you back.

103
00:10:58,279 --> 00:11:00,159
Such injuries are trivial for a demon.

104
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:01,799
I know it's nothing to you.

105
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:03,639
With your spiritual root intact,

106
00:11:03,879 --> 00:11:04,480
you could control others' minds

107
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,279
without entering dreams.

108
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,080
How could you be hurt?

109
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,799
But you're a mortal now.

110
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,279
If you walk down the street

111
00:11:11,519 --> 00:11:13,039
as if nothing happened after this,

112
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:14,720
it will arouse suspicion.

113
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:17,519
Go.

114
00:11:17,759 --> 00:11:18,679
I'll handle this.

115
00:11:29,679 --> 00:11:30,919
I've cast a spell.

116
00:11:31,399 --> 00:11:33,679
You can stay in these two bodies for a while

117
00:11:33,879 --> 00:11:34,720
without being recognized.

118
00:11:40,679 --> 00:11:42,200
If anyone asks, just say

119
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:44,399
Bai Weiran, the banker, came to rescue.

120
00:11:44,519 --> 00:11:45,679
You accepted the money

121
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:46,759
[and agreed to let her go.]

122
00:12:06,279 --> 00:12:07,360
Where is Meng Li?

123
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,240
She's...

124
00:12:09,759 --> 00:12:10,559
She's...

125
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:17,279
Tell me if you don't want to die.

126
00:12:17,279 --> 00:12:19,039
Bai Weiran came to ask for her.

127
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:21,720
We took the money and agreed to let her go.

128
00:12:24,039 --> 00:12:25,360
It's him again.

129
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:39,799
Where are we going?

130
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,159
To the Prince Xian's Mansion.

131
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:48,600
[In the hundred years you were asleep,]

132
00:12:49,519 --> 00:12:50,320
[I carried you on my back.]

133
00:12:52,159 --> 00:12:53,799
[I wished you could talk to me]

134
00:12:54,039 --> 00:12:55,159
[and go to the places we wanted]

135
00:12:55,679 --> 00:12:57,360
[to go to.]

136
00:12:58,519 --> 00:12:59,360
[Bai Weiran,]

137
00:13:01,519 --> 00:13:02,320
[thank you.]

138
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,600
[Now you're talking,]

139
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:07,440
[but not what I want to hear.]

140
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:09,639
[And you're going]

141
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,559
[to a place I don't want to go.]

142
00:13:12,759 --> 00:13:13,559
[A'Li,]

143
00:13:14,879 --> 00:13:15,679
[I'll wait for you.]
